12
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,879
Why did he bring a child along with him?

13
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,120
That's right.

14
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,199
And then he didn't

15
00:01:52,199 --> 00:01:53,239
tell anyone about it.

16
00:01:54,639 --> 00:01:56,080
A perfect good child,

17
00:01:56,080 --> 00:01:57,720
just died here so suddenly.

18
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:58,959
It's just getting us

19
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,599
implicated for no reason.

20
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,599
It is all my fault.

21
00:02:06,639 --> 00:02:07,959
But Master Ming, there is no need to be worried.

22
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,119
He brought that person here.

23
00:02:10,399 --> 00:02:11,639
The two of us, we didn't know anything.

24
00:02:13,160 --> 00:02:14,520
It's easy for you to say that.

25
00:02:15,559 --> 00:02:16,279
It's a son of the legal wife

26
00:02:16,279 --> 00:02:17,720
in the Marquis' household that's dead.

27
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:21,080
Today, the repose period is complete.

28
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,600
Late Eldest Uncle, your noble spirit is still present.

29
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,880
It's time to rest in the blessed place

30
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:29,119
and safeguard our family.

31
00:02:31,679 --> 00:02:32,399
Raise the funeral banner.

32
00:02:33,399 --> 00:02:35,360
Bring the funeral banner! Lead the way!

33
00:02:37,039 --> 00:02:39,080
Bring the funeral banner! Lead the way!

34
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:41,320
Shatter the crockery! Raise the casket!

35
