38
00:02:50,759 --> 00:02:52,399
Has everyone in the First Master's household died?

39
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:55,800
Who's that? Who!

40
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:04,119
You're a senile wet nurse,

41
00:03:04,119 --> 00:03:05,279
what nonsense are you spouting!

42
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,199
Eldest Young Master Bai,

43
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,759
you are the eldest son of the Second Master.

44
00:03:09,759 --> 00:03:10,639
You have nothing to do

45
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:11,360
with the household of the First Master Bai.

46
00:03:11,839 --> 00:03:13,440
We have someone of our own to start the procession.

47
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:15,199
Brother, why are you talking to her?

48
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,679
Where did this crazy woman come from?

49
00:03:16,679 --> 00:03:17,600
Drag her out.

50
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,320
Drag her out.

51
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,320
Just do it!

52
00:03:19,399 --> 00:03:20,199
What are you doing?

53
00:03:20,199 --> 00:03:21,279
Stop!

54
00:03:21,279 --> 00:03:22,479
Let me go! Let go!

55
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,440
Stop!

56
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:26,279
Young Master?

57
00:03:26,279 --> 00:03:26,839
Zhonghuai?

58
00:03:26,839 --> 00:03:27,399
He didn't die?

59
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,720
Zhonghuai!

60
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:30,639
Bai Ye? What...?

61
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,399
You're not dead.

62
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,080
It's Gu Tingye!

63
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:39,520
This is great. This is really great!

64
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,800
Such merriment in a mourning hall!

65
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,679
What do you intend to do by this?

66
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,440
It's the Young Master Gu.

67
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,960
How could you come so late!

68
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:50,639
These bastards, they have no respect for the law,

69
00:03:50,839 --> 00:03:52,600
they want to steal the inheritance!

70
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,559
My family is conducting funeral proceedings,

71
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,919
yet you come in here crying,

72
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:58,880
screaming and making merry.

73
00:03:58,880 --> 00:03:59,800
What are your intentions?

74
00:04:00,119 --> 00:04:02,199
Men, throw them out!

75
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,000
He's our First Household's Young Master.

76
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,559
You dare to kick him out?

77
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:07,399
Kick him out!

78
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,479
Quick.

79
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,759
Kick him out!

80
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,440
What are all of you doing? Bastards!

81
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,039
Young Master Ye! Young Master Ye!

82
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:14,720
Stop beating him!

83
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:16,799
Stop! Stop!

84
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,679
Stop fighting!

85
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,440
All of you stop!

86
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,440
What are you doing?

87
00:04:22,559 --> 00:04:24,399
Stop! Stop!

88
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:27,880
This is a mourning hall. Look at what it has become.

89
00:04:38,079 --> 00:04:39,480
It's unbelievable that Uncles from the branches

90
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,040
forbid the grandson from paying his respects.

91
00:04:41,799 --> 00:04:43,519
I have my late maternal grandfather's personal letter,

92
00:04:44,359 --> 00:04:45,440
clearly naming me as the rightful heir!

93
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,000
Why can I not be here?

94
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:47,880
Bullshit!

95
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:49,679
You are of the Gu family,

96
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:50,640
we are the Bai family.

97
00:04:51,760 --> 00:04:53,119
Who's ever heard someone from a different house

98
00:04:53,119 --> 00:04:54,239
got named as the heir!

99
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,799
Can it be that

100
00:04:56,799 --> 00:04:58,799
you intend to seize the Bai's fortune by force

101
00:04:59,160 --> 00:04:59,920
just based on the fact that

102
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,119
your father and brother are decorated nobles?

103
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:03,519
Assembled gentlemen,

104
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,200
venerable elders,

105
00:05:08,359 --> 00:05:09,679
please have a look at this letter and then decide.

106
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:32,239
I know my time is short.

107
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:39,079
I only hope you can inherit the family business,

108
00:05:39,679 --> 00:05:42,600
so as to not let it be lost by others' hands.

109
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,519
Hence I write this last letter.

110
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:47,720
Your Maternal Grandfather Bai. Awaiting your return.

111
00:05:47,799 --> 00:05:49,279
It's true.

112
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,000
This is simply nonsense.

113
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,239
That's right.

114
00:05:52,799 --> 00:05:54,279
I have never heard of such a letter!

115
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:54,920
Yes.

116
00:05:55,679 --> 00:05:57,839
It could be written by anyone.

117
00:05:57,839 --> 00:05:59,720
Who couldn't write such a letter?

118
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:01,480
You think you can take over

119
00:06:01,559 --> 00:06:02,440
the largest salt business in Yangzhou

120
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,600
with just a lousy letter like that?

121
00:06:06,119 --> 00:06:08,200
There would be letters and notes left around the house,

122
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:10,079
so would all the venerable elders please be witnesses?

123
00:06:10,799 --> 00:06:12,399
We can find some notes, compare the handwriting,

124
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,679
and check whether it's authentic or not.

125
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,880
With me,

126
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,799
I have some poems the old Master gifted me.

127
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,200
I was going to burn them

128
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,559
before the altar as an offering to the spirits.

129
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,239
Never thought they could be of this kind of use.

130
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:27,119
Take it.

131
00:06:33,359 --> 00:06:34,359
What letter?

132
00:06:34,359 --> 00:06:35,760
I have never heard of this!

133
00:06:36,119 --> 00:06:37,160
Before he passed away,

134
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,399
Uncle said I was resolute and capable.

135
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:41,119
He personally handed the salt business to me.

136
00:06:41,359 --> 00:06:42,440
Everyone in the Bai family saw that.

137
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:43,399
Isn't that so?

138
00:06:43,399 --> 00:06:45,160
Yes, we saw it.

139
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:45,920
That is right.

140
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:46,559
Uncle!

141
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,959
Look at my maternal grandfather's memorial tablet.

142
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,000
Look at him.

143
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,359
He's looking at you from heaven!

144
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,079
Swear to him

145
00:06:54,799 --> 00:06:56,440
that if anything you just said was false,

146
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:59,279
then the family shrine will be shaken with unrest,

147
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,600
and your deceased mother's spirit will not rest in peace!

148
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,480
County Magistrate,

149
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,880
we invited you to lead the funeral proceedings,

150
00:07:05,119 --> 00:07:06,679
how could you instead shield each other?

151
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:08,239
If you don't dare to swear,

152
00:07:08,239 --> 00:07:09,160
I dare!

153
00:07:10,079 --> 00:07:11,880
I, Gu Tingye, swear to heaven.

154
00:07:12,359 --> 00:07:14,839
It's true that I have been named as the heir.

155
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:17,200
Should anything be false,

156
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,959
then the family shrine of mine will be shaken with unrest,

157
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:21,359
and my deceased mother's spirit will not rest in peace.

158
00:07:21,959 --> 00:07:22,760
Uncle,

159
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,320
do you dare to swear on your deceased mother?

160
00:07:25,559 --> 00:07:28,239
You... you are just a scoundrel.

161
00:07:29,399 --> 00:07:31,119
The heaven and earth,

162
00:07:31,119 --> 00:07:31,920
passing spirits

163
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,119
and spiritual officials on duty today,

164
00:07:34,119 --> 00:07:35,760
they are all watching us!

165
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:39,119
Uncle, why do you not dare to swear?

166
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:41,600
I will say it then.

167
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,399
I...

168
00:07:44,399 --> 00:07:45,399
Bai Tingyu

169
00:07:45,399 --> 00:07:46,440
I swear to heaven.

170
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:50,160
It's true that I have been named as the heir.

171
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,519
Should anything be false,

172
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,279
then the family shrine...

173
00:07:58,239 --> 00:07:59,119
then the... family shrine...

174
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,640
Watch your tongue!

175
00:08:03,239 --> 00:08:04,239
He is a well-known delinquent

176
00:08:04,239 --> 00:08:05,839
in Bianjing City.

177
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:07,760
A notable scoundrel

178
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:09,239
among the wealthy young nobles.

179
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,279
He dares to voice such blasphemy

180
00:08:11,279 --> 00:08:12,160
against the family shrine.

181
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:14,519
Have all your years of education

182
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:15,480
gone to waste

183
00:08:16,119 --> 00:08:17,440
that you will compete with him

184
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,600
on how boorish one can be?

185
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,440
Sorry, father, you are correct.

186
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:21,880
Hypocrites, all of you.

187
00:08:22,239 --> 00:08:23,559
Always quoting

188
00:08:23,559 --> 00:08:24,440
the Sage's words,

189
00:08:25,279 --> 00:08:26,799
yet you speak nothing

190
00:08:26,799 --> 00:08:27,959
but lies and try to fool the people.

191
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:30,959
Venerable elders and officials,

192
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:33,200
I have worked in this household my whole life.

193
00:08:33,719 --> 00:08:34,799
I know best where everything is.

194
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,640
I'll take everyone to find

195
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,280
where my Master's letters and notes are.

196
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,320
Old crone!

197
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,960
This is the Bai's family manor!

198
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,679
You just wield some lies here

199
00:08:45,239 --> 00:08:46,960
with a few officials backing you up.

200
00:08:47,719 --> 00:08:49,320
So you want to just search and confiscate all you want?

201
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,640
If you want to get in

202
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:52,200
this courtyard today,

203
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,960
you can step over my dead body!

204
00:08:54,719 --> 00:08:55,760
Return the slave contracts!

205
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,479
Return them to us!

206
00:08:57,679 --> 00:08:59,520
Return the slave contracts.

207
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:01,039
Our master has passed away,

208
00:09:01,039 --> 00:09:02,440
and you took away our slave contracts.

209
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:04,919
Return them to us.

