Return the slave contracts to us.

216
00:09:17,359 --> 00:09:18,039
Stop creating a scene.

217
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:19,400
Return the slave contracts to us.

218
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,400
All of you

219
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,359
are Yangzhou's leading figures.

220
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:26,760
We went to admire the flowers

221
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:27,919
at the Zen Temple last time

222
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:29,400
and enjoyed together fine wines.

223
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:31,960
How about we all go look together,

224
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,320
treating it as a leisure outing?

225
00:09:36,119 --> 00:09:36,919
My lord.

226
00:09:37,599 --> 00:09:38,320
I'm going.

227
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:39,239
This way, please.

228
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,679
Please.

229
00:09:40,679 --> 00:09:41,559
Let's go. Quickly now!

230
00:09:47,159 --> 00:09:49,159
Who died in the river then?

231
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:52,239
My junior manservant, Zhique.

232
00:09:52,719 --> 00:09:54,280
I switched into his clothes

233
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:55,359
to carry on as him.

234
00:09:55,799 --> 00:09:56,840
You should have come to me when you escaped.

235
00:09:57,479 --> 00:09:58,440
These days,

236
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,559
I haven't had a good sleep.

237
00:10:00,239 --> 00:10:01,640
I didn't know how much more treachery awaited me.

238
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,919
If I showed myself, I would implicate you instead.

239
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,679
Now the truth is out and it's alright now,

240
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:07,119
so be at ease.

241
00:10:28,400 --> 00:10:29,840
It's the same.

242
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,679
Isn't it the same?

243
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:39,119
All of you elders, what do you think?

244
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,679
Brother Changli, what do you think?

245
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:48,760
The handwriting looks similar

246
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:51,000
but it's hard to identify for sure.

247
00:10:55,599 --> 00:10:57,799
I think the result is self-evident.

248
00:10:59,239 --> 00:11:00,039
Everyone assembled...

249
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:04,400
It is simply a joke!

250
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,080
This is the livelihood of hundreds

251
00:11:06,119 --> 00:11:07,520
in the Bai House.

252
00:11:08,239 --> 00:11:10,080
We pray to our ancestors and shrines four seasons.

253
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,359
There are schoolchildren and primary schools

254
00:11:11,359 --> 00:11:12,440
and acres of charity farmlands for our hopeless ones .

255
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,880
Our offspring's future all depend on this.

256
00:11:15,239 --> 00:11:16,039
It's not just his

257
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:17,119
