258
00:11:17,119 --> 00:11:17,840
That's right.

259
00:11:18,599 --> 00:11:19,679
Furthermore,

260
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,280
His Eldest Uncle has been sick in bed for a long time.

261
00:11:21,719 --> 00:11:23,280
I believe he was confused,

262
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:24,359
so let we three houses

263
00:11:24,359 --> 00:11:25,640
discuss it thoroughly instead!

264
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:28,000
You're a bunch of filthy brutes!

265
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,919
You live at his house and covet his assets.

266
00:11:30,359 --> 00:11:31,200
This family business

267
00:11:31,599 --> 00:11:32,559
was all built up

268
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,080
all by my master himself!

269
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:36,159
You noticed he was well-off

270
00:11:36,159 --> 00:11:37,119
so you came one by one to seek refuge.

271
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,400
When he's gone,

272
00:11:38,679 --> 00:11:40,200
you plot to steal his assets

273
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,320
and oppress his child.

274
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,599
Your conscience has been eaten by dogs!

275
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:45,440
What the hell?

276
00:11:45,479 --> 00:11:46,119
What are you saying?

277
00:11:46,119 --> 00:11:47,159
How could you say this?

278
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,760
In order to preserve you elders' reputations,

279
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:52,679
I did not pull out another letter I have.

280
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,919
