Where did that monkey come from

564
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:10,280
to make such loud ruckus?

565
00:27:10,319 --> 00:27:12,560
Hurry and save a life!

566
00:27:12,599 --> 00:27:13,880
Hurry up. Leave now.

567
00:27:14,479 --> 00:27:15,760
Don't wake him up.

568
00:27:15,959 --> 00:27:17,839
Come, leave.

569
00:27:17,839 --> 00:27:18,719
Lord Magistrate Sheng's house.

570
00:27:18,719 --> 00:27:19,839
May the physician hurry and save a life!

571
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:20,959
The physician is inside!

572
00:27:22,560 --> 00:27:23,599
Somebody help!

573
00:27:23,599 --> 00:27:24,479
You can't barge in.

574
00:27:24,599 --> 00:27:25,119
I'm warning you!

575
00:27:26,439 --> 00:27:27,439
Master.

576
00:27:27,439 --> 00:27:28,520
I'll go get a prescription first.

577
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:29,920
Get my medicine box!

578
00:27:29,959 --> 00:27:30,640
Don't just stand there.

579
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:31,719
It's child delivery. Go!

580
00:27:33,239 --> 00:27:34,319
This...this horse?

581
00:27:34,560 --> 00:27:35,520
Get on the horse!

582
00:27:45,359 --> 00:27:46,040
Take care, Master.

583
00:27:46,959 --> 00:27:48,439
This is Magistrate Sheng's daughter.

584
00:27:48,439 --> 00:27:49,160
Watch her well for me.

585
00:27:49,800 --> 00:27:51,319
My carriage will come to fetch her.

586
00:27:51,319 --> 00:27:52,079
Bring the medicine

587
00:27:52,079 --> 00:27:52,959
and bring two clerks

588
00:27:52,959 --> 00:27:53,800
to come to Sheng House.

589
00:28:09,560 --> 00:28:11,760
This thing with your house is no small matter.

590
00:28:26,800 --> 00:28:27,560
Open the door!

591
00:28:33,079 --> 00:28:35,119
These old bones of mine

592
00:28:35,119 --> 00:28:37,119
are all jolted to pieces.

593
00:28:37,119 --> 00:28:40,000
I usually only ride on donkeys.

594
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:42,599
This horse is too high. Too high!

595
00:28:50,079 --> 00:28:51,239
What are you doing?

596
00:29:30,599 --> 00:29:32,880
Isn't that the act of a burglar?

597
00:29:36,359 --> 00:29:38,400
In broad daylight? Climbing over the wall?

598
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,359
Ridiculous.

599
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:53,599
The door is open.

600
00:29:54,400 --> 00:29:56,079
Master Doctor,

601
00:29:56,079 --> 00:29:57,199
let's go!

602
00:29:58,920 --> 00:30:01,359
Slow down.

603
00:30:02,280 --> 00:30:03,280
You old turd!

604
00:30:03,280 --> 00:30:04,599
How dare you barge into women's inner chambers.

605
00:30:05,599 --> 00:30:07,160
You're just a common man

606
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:08,560
and how dare you barge into an official's manor?

607
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:10,599
Attendants! Come quickly

608
00:30:10,599 --> 00:30:11,439
and take this man to the Magistrate.

609
00:30:31,119 --> 00:30:32,920
I'm from the Gu's, the Marquis Manor of Dongjing.

610
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:34,880
You'd better not mistake me for somebody else.

611
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:37,000
in full broad daylight,

612
00:30:37,000 --> 00:30:37,920
