615
00:30:43,439 --> 00:30:44,160
It's a woman's matter.

616
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:45,839
How can we let a male physician come in?

617
00:30:50,479 --> 00:30:52,040
Her breathing is so weak.

618
00:30:52,040 --> 00:30:52,880
It's already too late

619
00:30:52,880 --> 00:30:53,839
even if I go in now!

620
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:55,760
You're a man. What are you trying to do?

621
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:57,400
Are you trying to taint the woman's honor?

622
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:03,239
You must preserve the woman in labor!

623
00:31:09,119 --> 00:31:09,880
Move aside.

624
00:31:25,959 --> 00:31:27,400
Pitiful child.

625
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:28,640
Go and see your mother now.

626
00:31:30,520 --> 00:31:32,359
Mother.

627
00:31:33,920 --> 00:31:34,599
Sixth Sister.

628
00:31:35,640 --> 00:31:37,640
Child, I can't work a miracle.

629
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:39,119
When I came,

630
00:31:39,119 --> 00:31:40,439
it was already too late.

631
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:43,000
The child is too big and it can't be born.

632
00:31:43,199 --> 00:31:44,479
It just dragged your mother to death

633
00:31:44,479 --> 00:31:45,800
along with it.

634
00:31:46,239 --> 00:31:47,880
You called me here too late!

635
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:51,239
The baby in her belly won't be able to make it too.

636
00:31:52,439 --> 00:31:53,280
Child, look at your mother.

637
00:31:58,319 --> 00:31:59,199
Mother.

638
00:32:04,839 --> 00:32:06,400
Come here.

639
00:32:06,400 --> 00:32:08,280
Lady,

640
00:32:08,280 --> 00:32:09,479
I'll prick a few needles in you.

641
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:10,760
Breathe

642
00:32:10,760 --> 00:32:12,640
