643
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:15,199
Mother.

644
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:20,920
Mother.

645
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,400
Mother.

646
00:32:42,479 --> 00:32:44,040
I don't have much time left.

647
00:32:47,319 --> 00:32:48,640
I'm so cold.

648
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:53,000
Warmer?

649
00:32:58,359 --> 00:32:59,439
It has been tough for you.

650
00:33:02,199 --> 00:33:03,680
How did you find the physician?

651
00:33:04,599 --> 00:33:06,800
I ran into the Young Master

652
00:33:06,800 --> 00:33:08,640
who played pot-pitching with me.

653
00:33:09,560 --> 00:33:11,280
Second Master Gu.

654
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:12,280
He rode the horse.

655
00:33:12,280 --> 00:33:14,680
And on his horse, he brought the physician here.

656
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:18,520
You must thank him properly.

657
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:25,160
That knee guard.

658
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:26,599
I've already finished embroidering it.

659
00:33:27,119 --> 00:33:29,359
Take that and give it to Master Bai.

660
00:33:31,560 --> 00:33:33,680
He helped you.

661
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:34,880
You must thank him.

662
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:35,640
Right?

663
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:38,839
Alright.

664
00:33:42,160 --> 00:33:44,439
I don't have anything much else either.

665
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:50,959
That scroll, with Lady Li guarding over Niangzi Pass.

666
00:33:52,839 --> 00:33:54,160
I embroidered it well.

667
00:33:56,119 --> 00:33:57,520
I'll leave it to you.

668
00:33:58,400 --> 00:34:02,880
Alright, Mother.

669
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:11,399
How pitiful you're so little.

670
00:34:13,520 --> 00:34:14,840
And you have to survive

671
00:34:14,879 --> 00:34:16,040
in this courtyard.

672
00:34:18,199 --> 00:34:19,560
I keep telling you,

673
00:34:21,239 --> 00:34:22,840
don't stand out.

674
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:26,760
You just refused to listen to me.

675
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:28,719
I was wrong.

676
00:34:29,159 --> 00:34:32,159
I will listen to you in the future.

677
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:35,679
I will listen to you.

678
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:38,800
Remember this.

679
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:41,959
Look at me.

680
00:34:46,479 --> 00:34:47,439
In all things,

681
00:34:51,399 --> 00:34:52,280
survival is of the utmost importance.

682
00:34:58,040 --> 00:34:59,199
Did you hear me?

683
00:35:00,479 --> 00:35:03,479
Mother, I will remember.

684
00:35:04,199 --> 00:35:07,080
I will always remember this.

685
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:09,639
What did you call me?

686
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:12,080
I can't bear to call you that.

687
00:35:12,760 --> 00:35:15,800
I don't want to call you "Mistress".

688
00:35:29,719 --> 00:35:30,919
Mistress...

689
00:35:33,560 --> 00:35:35,919
Mistress Wei.

690
00:35:39,600 --> 00:35:41,040
Well done.

691
00:35:45,399 --> 00:35:46,879
That's good.

692
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:52,280
When I'm no longer with you in the future,

693
00:35:55,639 --> 00:35:57,320
you will be left alone

694
00:35:58,959 --> 00:36:01,479
in this courtyard.

695
00:36:03,479 --> 00:36:05,520
You will be the alone.

696
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:09,399
Your daughter will go to Grandmother's.

697
00:36:11,159 --> 00:36:12,239
Alright.

698
00:36:25,479 --> 00:36:28,399
Mother! Mother!

699
00:36:29,639 --> 00:36:34,320
Mother! Mother!

700
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:40,360
Mother! Mother...

701
00:37:44,679 --> 00:37:45,840
From now on,

702
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:49,399
I will never have Mistress Wei.

703
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:53,439
I don't have my birth mother either.

704
00:37:55,399 --> 00:37:57,679
You will be alone in the future.

705
00:37:57,679 --> 00:37:58,639
You must cherish yourself.

706
00:38:06,919 --> 00:38:07,800
Ming Lan!

707
00:38:07,879 --> 00:38:08,959
Sixth Sister!

708
00:38:09,679 --> 00:38:10,399
Minglan!

709
00:38:10,439 --> 00:38:11,120
Let me see.

710
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:13,199
Go and get water now.

711
00:38:13,199 --> 00:38:13,919
Hurry and get help!

712
00:38:13,919 --> 00:38:14,600
Get some towel.

713
00:38:14,600 --> 00:38:15,239
Get my medicines!

714
00:38:33,280 --> 00:38:35,239
You dumb bastard!

715
00:38:35,879 --> 00:38:38,000
How many maidservants do we have that we needed

716
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:39,199
that midwife to go

717
00:38:39,199 --> 00:38:40,159
and tend to the water?

718
00:38:40,600 --> 00:38:41,360
She bullied you

719
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:43,040
for being born such a fool!

720
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:45,439
You even believed such lies?

721
00:38:49,600 --> 00:38:50,360
Lin Qinshuang

722
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:52,560
was your superficial master,

723
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:54,159
but I'm your real boss!

724
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:55,520
In this family,

725
00:38:55,520 --> 00:38:56,959
you're a lead maidservant.

726
00:38:56,959 --> 00:38:57,959
Yet you didn't order others,

727
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,080
but you went and got yourself controlled

728
00:38:59,080 --> 00:39:00,439
by that whore?

729
00:39:02,040 --> 00:39:04,000
You are a damned fool!

730
00:39:04,439 --> 00:39:05,239
Why didn't your parents

731
00:39:05,239 --> 00:39:06,239
give you half a brain at least?

732
00:39:10,919 --> 00:39:11,560
Mother.

733
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:14,000
You are here.

734
00:39:16,040 --> 00:39:17,280
I have something to say to my mother.

735
00:39:17,959 --> 00:39:18,840
Tell her to leave first.

736
00:39:19,919 --> 00:39:20,600
Get lost!

737
00:39:29,919 --> 00:39:30,679
I haven't cried yet.

738
00:39:30,679 --> 00:39:32,080
Why are you crying?

739
00:39:32,439 --> 00:39:33,000
Cool down.

740
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:35,280
Listen to that.

741
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,560
Such mess like cow manure!

742
00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:40,360
I exhausted myself

743
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:42,399
to stuff her into Lin Qinshuang's courtyard.

744
00:39:42,959 --> 00:39:44,280
But she was so useless,

745
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:45,639
and gave me this instead!

746
00:39:46,239 --> 00:39:46,959
She's forcing me

747
00:39:46,959 --> 00:39:48,280
to see the King of Hell soon.

748
00:39:57,760 --> 00:40:03,080
I'm innocent, Master.

749
00:40:03,360 --> 00:40:05,159
She's my servant.

750
00:40:05,239 --> 00:40:06,159
It's all my fault.

751
00:40:06,159 --> 00:40:07,760
Please tell Dongrong not to beat her anymore.

752
00:40:07,840 --> 00:40:09,120
Tell him to stop.

753
00:40:09,639 --> 00:40:10,120
Master.

754
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:13,120
That damned midwife!

755
00:40:13,120 --> 00:40:14,000
Beat her!

756
00:40:15,239 --> 00:40:16,360
I'm wrongly accused, Master.

757
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:18,600
Beat her until the number is complete!

758
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:30,479
Master, I finished twenty strokes of flogging.

759
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:38,199
Useless whore!

760
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:40,760
Drag her out and give her back to her parents!

761
00:40:45,719 --> 00:40:46,840
May your anger dissipate, Master.

762
00:40:54,399 --> 00:40:55,639
Master. Mistress.

763
00:40:55,639 --> 00:40:57,760
It's totally my fault.

764
00:40:58,560 --> 00:41:00,040
I am young and inexperienced.

765
00:41:00,639 --> 00:41:02,120
I just didn't know that

766
00:41:02,120 --> 00:41:03,399
a baby that big

767
00:41:04,040 --> 00:41:05,439
couldn't be born.

768
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:08,479
I failed to save Sister Wei.

769
00:41:10,840 --> 00:41:12,239
May your anger be dissipated, Master.

770
00:41:13,320 --> 00:41:17,159
May your anger be dissipated, Master.

