00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:19,320
May your anger be dissipated, Master.

772
00:41:21,600 --> 00:41:23,879
Mistress Lin!

773
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:26,439
Shuang'er. Shuang'er!

774
00:41:26,879 --> 00:41:27,760
What's wrong, Shuang'er?

775
00:41:29,159 --> 00:41:30,120
Get the physician.

776
00:41:30,399 --> 00:41:31,000
Yes.

777
00:41:31,719 --> 00:41:34,760
Shuang'er. Shuang'er.

778
00:41:34,959 --> 00:41:36,600
How are you going to arrange

779
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:37,280
Mistress Wei's funeral?

780
00:41:41,560 --> 00:41:43,120
She was just a concubine sold here.

781
00:41:43,120 --> 00:41:44,560
What funeral?

782
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:46,879
Just go and order a coffin from the street.

783
00:41:47,439 --> 00:41:48,719
In consideration of her death being a result

784
00:41:49,479 --> 00:41:50,919
from her trying to expand Sheng House's heirs.

785
00:41:51,520 --> 00:41:53,280
Find a scribe with good penmanship to write a tablet,

786
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:55,159
and give her parents' family five a quarter kilo of silver.

787
00:41:55,159 --> 00:41:56,439
Have Mother Liu arrange it.

788
00:41:57,280 --> 00:41:58,239
But Mother,

789
00:41:58,239 --> 00:41:59,560
as the Madam of this family,

790
00:42:00,080 --> 00:42:01,639
arranging the concubine's funeral personally

791
00:42:01,639 --> 00:42:02,679
is the approach.

792
00:42:03,040 --> 00:42:04,120
Or else the word will get out,

793
00:42:04,719 --> 00:42:06,159
and Sheng family's reputation

794
00:42:06,159 --> 00:42:07,280
will be unsightly.

795
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:11,239
Fine then.

796
00:42:11,239 --> 00:42:12,360
I'll make myself an example

797
00:42:12,360 --> 00:42:13,280
to that whore.

798
00:42:13,879 --> 00:42:14,439
Let her see

799
00:42:14,479 --> 00:42:16,399
what it means to be the Madam of a house!

800
00:42:18,399 --> 00:42:19,159
By the way, Hua'er,

801
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:20,959
This time when I went back,

802
00:42:20,959 --> 00:42:21,879
your uncle gave me

803
00:42:21,879 --> 00:42:22,600
two strands of pearls.

804
00:42:23,320 --> 00:42:25,159
Mother, sit down now.

805
00:42:25,879 --> 00:42:27,199
Forget the pearls.

806
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:29,439
Just listen to me.

807
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:31,239
You must not throw any tantrums

808
00:42:31,239 --> 00:42:32,600
in the courtyard in the future.

809
00:42:33,679 --> 00:42:34,840
If father comes to look for you,

810
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:36,439
you just say

811
00:42:36,439 --> 00:42:38,239
how pitiful Mistress Wei was and how unlucky.

812
00:42:38,800 --> 00:42:40,600
As for the rest, don't say anything.

813
00:42:41,959 --> 00:42:43,080
Then...

814
00:42:43,080 --> 00:42:45,120
I shouldn't ask for the keys to manage the house?

815
00:42:45,120 --> 00:42:46,840
Don't ever talk about this.

816
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:47,840
We should console father

817
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:49,439
during this period.

818
00:42:50,840 --> 00:42:51,959
That whore Lin Qinshuang

819
00:42:51,959 --> 00:42:53,600
caused this havoc.

820
00:42:53,679 --> 00:42:54,439
Why can't I ride on this chance

821
00:42:54,439 --> 00:42:56,840
to get back the house keys?

822
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:58,320
Mother, listen to my advice.

823
00:42:58,399 --> 00:42:59,159
These days,

824
00:42:59,159 --> 00:43:00,840
don't think about packing up

825
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:02,719
and the trip to Dongjing.

826
00:43:02,719 --> 00:43:04,280
Just keep your devotion

827
00:43:04,320 --> 00:43:05,679
into managing the funeral.

828
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:09,679
How should I do it?

829
00:43:11,280 --> 00:43:12,479
Bury the Mistress Wei generously.

830
00:43:12,879 --> 00:43:14,320
Treat Mistress Wei's family generously.

831
00:43:24,479 --> 00:43:25,120
Did Master ask me

832
00:43:25,120 --> 00:43:25,959
for the keys?

833
00:43:26,959 --> 00:43:27,639
It's not that.

834
00:43:28,120 --> 00:43:29,040
Master hired

835
00:43:29,040 --> 00:43:30,239
a new physician for you.

836
00:43:30,840 --> 00:43:31,719
Dongrong is with him.

837
00:43:31,800 --> 00:43:32,760
Waiting outside the door.

838
00:43:35,479 --> 00:43:36,360
Invite him in now.

839
00:43:40,080 --> 00:43:41,919
Zulou and Ms Gan's are grateful.

840
00:43:42,399 --> 00:43:43,600
This is their gratitude.

841
00:43:45,239 --> 00:43:46,600
It's just my duty.

842
00:43:46,600 --> 00:43:48,239
You don't need to bother.

843
00:43:53,199 --> 00:43:54,719
Mistress Wei's family sent someone here.
